com.ianywhere.ultralitejni12
Interface TableSchema

public interface TableSchema

Specifies the schema of a table and provides constants defining the names of system tables. As of version 12, this interface only contains table-related constants. They include system table names, table flags, and types of data in sysuldata.

TABLE_IS_SYSTEM

static final short TABLE_IS_SYSTEM
Bit flag denoting a table is a system table. This value can be logically combined with other flags in the table_flags column of the SYS_TABLES table.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

TABLE_IS_NOSYNC

static final short TABLE_IS_NOSYNC
Bit flag denoting a table is a no-sync table (table that is never synchronized). This value can be logically combined with other flags in the table_flags column of the SYS_TABLES table except TABLE_IS_DOWNLOAD_ONLY.

See Also:
